{"type":"message","id":"fd1d5173","parentId":"0508df1b","timestamp":"2026-07-03T06:59:40.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1b9bd1df42c24777884642f2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"IMAGE_PATH=\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/alibaba-token-chart-1783061938.png\"\nPOST_TEXT=\"𝗔𝗹𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗯𝗮 𝗷𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝗰𝘂𝘁 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼𝗸𝗲𝗻 𝘂𝘀𝗲 𝗯𝘆 𝟵𝟵%.\n\nMost AI agents choke when you hand them thousands of tools.\n\nThey load EVERYTHING into context. Burn through tokens. Get slow. Expensive. Unreliable.\n\nAlibaba's new framework does something different:\n\nIt skips loading every tool. Instead of stuffing the entire toolbox into context, it routes to the right tool on demand.\n\nResult? 99% less token waste.\n\nHere's why this matters:\n\nThe current AI agent trend is \\\"give it more tools.\\\" More APIs. More capabilities. More context bloat.\n\nThat's why your agents are slow and expensive.\n\nThe future isn't more tools in context. It's smarter routing to fewer tools.\n\nIf your agent needs to \\\"know\\\" 500 tools to do its job — you've built it wrong. You've built a search engine, not an agent.\n\nWhat's the maximum number of tools an agent should actually have loaded?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #Efficiency #Alibaba #TokenOptimization\"\n\n/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \"264468965\" image \"$IMAGE_PATH\" \"$POST_TEXT\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"IMAGE_PATH=\\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/alibaba-token-chart-1783061938.png\\\"\\nPOST_TEXT=\\\"𝗔𝗹𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗯𝗮 𝗷𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝗰𝘂𝘁 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼𝗸𝗲𝗻 𝘂𝘀𝗲 𝗯𝘆 𝟵𝟵%.\\n\\nMost AI agents choke when you hand them thousands of tools.\\n\\nThey load EVERYTHING into context. Burn through tokens. Get slow. Expensive. Unreliable.\\n\\nAlibaba's new framework does something different:\\n\\nIt skips loading every tool. Instead of stuffing the entire toolbox into context, it routes to the right tool on demand.\\n\\nResult? 99% less token waste.\\n\\nHere's why this matters:\\n\\nThe current AI agent trend is \\\\\\\"give it more tools.\\\\\\\" More APIs. More capabilities. More context bloat.\\n\\nThat's why your agents are slow and expensive.\\n\\nThe future isn't more tools in context. It's smarter routing to fewer tools.\\n\\nIf your agent needs to \\\\\\\"know\\\\\\\" 500 tools to do its job — you've built it wrong. You've built a search engine, not an agent.\\n\\nWhat's the maximum number of tools an agent should actually have loaded?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #Efficiency #Alibaba #TokenOptimization\\\"\\n\\n/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \\\"264468965\\\" image \\\"$IMAGE_PATH\\\" \\\"$POST_TEXT\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783061952562,"responseId":"wV1Hat_0HrOAvPgPoOzJgAc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2039bdd5","parentId":"fd1d5173","timestamp":"2026-07-03T06:59:42.440Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1b9bd1df42c24777884642f2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK: https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7478704001279188992/\nDISPLAY_NAME: Andrii Bidochko\nCHARS: 1007"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2117,"aggregated":"OK: https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7478704001279188992/\nDISPLAY_NAME: Andrii Bidochko\nCHARS: 1007","cwd":"/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783061982437}}
{"type":"message","id":"f60e13d6","parentId":"2039bdd5","timestamp":"2026-07-03T06:59:53.167Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8274baf1336d48fda272ba26","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Alibaba just cut AI agent token use by 99%\n\n**Published:** 2026-07-03T06:59:45Z\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7478704001279188992/\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7478704001279188992\n**Format:** image\n**Characters:** 1007\n**Pillar:** Technology & AI innovations\n**Image:** /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/alibaba-token-chart-1783061938.png\n\n## Post Body\n\n𝗔𝗹𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗯𝗮 𝗷𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝗰𝘂𝘁 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼𝗸𝗲𝗻 𝘂𝘀𝗲 𝗯𝘆 𝟵𝟵%.\n\nMost AI agents choke when you hand them thousands of tools.\n\nThey load EVERYTHING into context. Burn through tokens. Get slow. Expensive. Unreliable.\n\nAlibaba's new framework does something different:\n\nIt skips loading every tool. Instead of stuffing the entire toolbox into context, it routes to the right tool on demand.\n\nResult? 99% less token waste.\n\nHere's why this matters:\n\nThe current AI agent trend is \"give it more tools.\" More APIs. More capabilities. More context bloat.\n\nThat's why your agents are slow and expensive.\n\nThe future isn't more tools in context. It's smarter routing to fewer tools.\n\nIf your agent needs to \"know\" 500 tools to do its job — you've built it wrong. You've built a search engine, not an agent.\n\nWhat's the maximum number of tools an agent should actually have loaded?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #Efficiency #Alibaba #TokenOptimization\n\n## Performance\n\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\n\n- **Impressions:** —\n- **Reactions:** —\n- **Comments:** —\n- **Shares:** —\n- **Last checked:** —\n","path":"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/posts/2026-07-03-alibaba-just-cut-ai-agent.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"content\": \"# Alibaba just cut AI agent token use by 99%\\n\\n**Published:** 2026-07-03T06:59:45Z\\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7478704001279188992/\\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7478704001279188992\\n**Format:** image\\n**Characters:** 1007\\n**Pillar:** Technology & AI innovations\\n**Image:** /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/alibaba-token-chart-1783061938.png\\n\\n## Post Body\\n\\n𝗔𝗹𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗯𝗮 𝗷𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝗰𝘂𝘁 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼𝗸𝗲𝗻 𝘂𝘀𝗲 𝗯𝘆 𝟵𝟵%.\\n\\nMost AI agents choke when you hand them thousands of tools.\\n\\nThey load EVERYTHING into context. Burn through tokens. Get slow. Expensive. Unreliable.\\n\\nAlibaba's new framework does something different:\\n\\nIt skips loading every tool. Instead of stuffing the entire toolbox into context, it routes to the right tool on demand.\\n\\nResult? 99% less token waste.\\n\\nHere's why this matters:\\n\\nThe current AI agent trend is \\\"give it more tools.\\\" More APIs. More capabilities. More context bloat.\\n\\nThat's why your agents are slow and expensive.\\n\\nThe future isn't more tools in context. It's smarter routing to fewer tools.\\n\\nIf your agent needs to \\\"know\\\" 500 tools to do its job — you've built it wrong. You've built a search engine, not an agent.\\n\\nWhat's the maximum number of tools an agent should actually have loaded?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #Efficiency #Alibaba #TokenOptimization\\n\\n## Performance\\n\\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\\n\\n- **Impressions:** —\\n- **Reactions:** —\\n- **Comments:** —\\n- **Shares:** —\\n- **Last checked:** —\\n\", \"path\": \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/posts/2026-07-03-alibaba-just-cut-ai-agent.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783061982446,"responseId":"311HaqLAIcn03PQPyKrR2AE"}}
