{"type":"message","id":"64a2ed54","parentId":"7dbf6e2f","timestamp":"2026-07-03T07:44:44.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Andrii — nice work on the Alibaba post! 🎯\n\nYou're showing up. That's the game.\n\nOne down, 1-2 more to hit your daily cadence. Here's a quick idea from your pillars:\n\n**Tech/AI angle:** The AI agent space is heating up — Cursor just raised at $400M valuation. How does that change the landscape for platforms like UBOS?\n\nWant to knock it out now?"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bd9eb9d5e3574236b6c5a122","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"Andrii — nice work on the Alibaba post! 🎯\n\nYou're showing up. That's the game.\n\nOne down, 1-2 more to hit your daily cadence. Here's a quick idea from your pillars:\n\n**Tech/AI angle:** The AI agent space is heating up — Cursor just raised at $400M valuation. How does that change the landscape for platforms like UBOS?\n\nWant to knock it out now?","presentation":{"blocks":[{"buttons":[{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"coach_write_cursor"},"label":"✍️ Write it now","style":"primary"},{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"coach_new_idea"},"label":"💡 Give me another idea"},{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"coach_later"},"label":"Later","style":"secondary"}],"type":"buttons"}]}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"send\", \"message\": \"Andrii — nice work on the Alibaba post! 🎯\\n\\nYou're showing up. That's the game.\\n\\nOne down, 1-2 more to hit your daily cadence. Here's a quick idea from your pillars:\\n\\n**Tech/AI angle:** The AI agent space is heating up — Cursor just raised at $400M valuation. How does that change the landscape for platforms like UBOS?\\n\\nWant to knock it out now?\", \"presentation\": {\"blocks\": [{\"buttons\": [{\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_write_cursor\"}, \"label\": \"✍️ Write it now\", \"style\": \"primary\"}, {\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_new_idea\"}, \"label\": \"💡 Give me another idea\"}, {\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_later\"}, \"label\": \"Later\", \"style\": \"secondary\"}], \"type\": \"buttons\"}]}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783064669887,"responseId":"X2hHaqzHFaTz3PQP-LCvWA"}}
