tes/rashishrivastava/2026/04/15/mercors-23-year-old-billionaire-founders-grapple-with-employee-fraud-and-north-korean-infiltration/[Mercor’s 23-Year-Old Billionaire Founders Grapple With Employee Fraud And North Korean Infiltration](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/2026/04/15/mercors-23-year-old-billionaire-founders-grapple-with-employee-fraud-and-north-korean-infiltration/)By[Rashi Shrivastava](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nand[Anna Tong](https://www.forbes.com/sites/annatong/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/annatong/2026/03/05/cursor-goes-to-war-for-ai-coding-dominance/[Cursor Goes To War For AI Coding Dominance](https://www.forbes.com/sites/annatong/2026/03/05/cursor-goes-to-war-for-ai-coding-dominance/)By[Rashi Shrivastava](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nand[Rashi Shrivastava](https://www.forbes.com/sites/rashishrivastava/),\\nForbes Staff\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/amyfeldman/2025/08/11/longer-leash-on-life-inside-the-dog-longevity-startup-loyal/[Longer Leash On Life: Inside The Dog Longevity Startup](https://www.forbes.com/sites/amyfeldman/2025/08/11/longer-leash-on-life-inside-the-dog-longevity-startup-loyal/)By[Amy Feldman](https://www.forbes.com/sites/amyfeldman/),\\nSenior Editor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/emilybaker-white/2025/08/18/with-trumps-tiktok-ban-on-hold-bytedance-is-quietly-launching-ai-apps/[With Trump’s TikTok Ban On Hold, ByteDance Is Quietly Launching AI Apps](https://www.forbes.com/sites/emilybaker-white/2025/08/18/with-trumps-tiktok-ban-on-hold-bytedance-is-quietly-launching-ai-apps/)By[Emily Baker-White](https://www.forbes.com/sites/emilybaker-white-1/),\\nSenior Writer\\n\\n[Can you solve today's phrase?](https://www.forbes.com/games/frase)\\n\\n## More From Innovation\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/brianmazique/2026/07/04/abdullah-mason-vs-albert-bell-full-cardwhat-time-does-it-start/\\n54 minutes ago\\n\\n### [Abdullah Mason Vs. Albert Bell Full Card - What Time Does It Start?](https://www.forbes.com/sites/brianmazique/2026/07/04/abdullah-mason-vs-albert-bell-full-cardwhat-time-does-it-start/)\\nAbdullah Mason defends his WBO lightweight title vs. Albert Bell in Cleveland on July 4. Here's the full card, start time, ring walks and how to watch The Fight.\\nBy[Brian Mazique](https://www.forbes.com/sites/brianmazique/),\\nContributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/brianmazique/2026/07/03/ufc-329-mcgregor-vs-holloway-whats-at-stake-and-everything-we-know/\\n2 hours ago\\n\\n### [UFC 329 McGregor Vs. Holloway: What's At Stake And Everything We Know](https://www.forbes.com/sites/brianmazique/2026/07/03/ufc-329-mcgregor-vs-holloway-whats-at-stake-and-everything-we-know/)\\nConor McGregor returns from a five-year layoff to rematch Max Holloway at UFC 329 on July 11. Here's what's at stake for both and everything to know about the card.\\nBy[Brian Mazique](https://www.forbes.com/sites/brianmazique/),\\nContributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/paultassi/2026/07/03/todays-nyt-strands-hints-spangram-answers-saturday-july-4-ooh/\\n4 hours ago\\n\\n### [Today’s NYT Strands Hints, Spangram, Answers: Saturday, July 4 (Ooh!)](https://www.forbes.com/sites/paultassi/2026/07/03/todays-nyt-strands-hints-spangram-answers-saturday-july-4-ooh/)\\nLooking for help with today's NYT Strands puzzle? Here's an extra hint to help you uncover the right words, as well as all of today's answers and Spangram.\\nBy[Paul Tassi](https://www.forbes.com/sites/paultassi/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2026/07/03/wordle-answer-saturday-july-4/\\n7 hours ago\\n\\n### [Today’s Wordle #1841 Hints And Answer For Saturday, July 4](https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2026/07/03/wordle-answer-saturday-july-4/)\\nLooking for help with today's New York Times Wordle? Here are some expert hints, clues and commentary to help you solve today's Wordle and sharpen your guessing game.\\nBy[Erik Kain](https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2026/07/03/nyt-pips-answers-saturday-july-4/\\n7 hours ago\\n\\n### [NYT ‘Pips’ Hints, Answers And Walkthrough For Saturday, July 4](https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2026/07/03/nyt-pips-answers-saturday-july-4/)\\nLooking for help with today's New York Times Pips? We'll walk you through today's puzzle and help you match dominoes to tiles.\\nBy[Erik Kain](https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/brucelee/2026/07/03/hydration-breaks-at-2026-world-cup-raise-controversy-for-fifa/\\n8 hours ago\\n\\n### [Hydration Breaks At 2026 World Cup Raise Controversy For FIFA](https://www.forbes.com/sites/brucelee/2026/07/03/hydration-breaks-at-2026-world-cup-raise-controversy-for-fifa/)\\nThe 2026 World Cup is the first one to have required hydration breaks during each half of the football matches. Here's why FIFA instituted these and the controversy.\\nBy[Bruce Y. Lee](https://www.forbes.com/sites/brucelee/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/ewanspence/2026/07/03/apple-news-headlines-iphone-18-pro-preorder-dates-new-ipad-pro-macbook-pro/\\n10 hours ago\\n\\n### [Apple Loop: iPhone 18 Pro Pre-Order Dates, New iPad Pro Details, iPhone 16e Special Offers](https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewanspence/2026/07/03/apple-news-headlines-iphone-18-pro-preorder-dates-new-ipad-pro-macbook-pro/)\\nThis week’s Apple headlines: iPhone 18 Pro pre-orders, Apple's significant data leak, iOS 27 dates, new iPad Pro and MacBook Pro details, refurbished iPhone 16e and more...\\nBy[Ewan Spence](https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewanspence/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/ewanspence/2026/07/03/android-news-headlines-galaxy-z-fold8-wide-honor-magic-v6-f-droid-oneplus-oppo/\\n10 hours ago\\n\\n### [Android Circuit: Galaxy Z Fold8 Wide Teased, Fighting For F-Droid, Magic V6 Arrives In UK](https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewanspence/2026/07/03/android-news-headlines-galaxy-z-fold8-wide-honor-magic-v6-f-droid-oneplus-oppo/)\\nThis week’s Android headlines: Galaxy Z Fold Wide teased, the final Galaxy Z Flip, Honor Magic V6 in the UK, OnePlus pushes Oppo brand, fighting for F-Droid and more...\\nBy[Ewan Spence](https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewanspence/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2026/07/03/what-to-watch-this-weekend-new-shows-and-movies-to-stream-on-netflix-hulu-prime-video-apple-tv-and-more/\\n10 hours ago\\n\\n### [What To Watch This Weekend: New Shows And Movies To Stream On Netflix, Hulu, Prime Video, Apple TV And More](https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2026/07/03/what-to-watch-this-weekend-new-shows-and-movies-to-stream-on-netflix-hulu-prime-video-apple-tv-and-more/)\\nLooking for something new to stream this weekend? Here’s every major new movie and show hitting Netflix, Hulu, Prime Video, Apple TV and more.\\nBy[Erik Kain](https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/),\\nSenior Contributor\\n\\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/johnwerner/2026/07/03/gearing-up-for-250-a-july-3-post/\\n12 hours ago\\n\\n### [Gearing Up For 250: A July 3 Post](https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnwerner/2026/07/03/gearing-up-for-250-a-july-3-post/)\\nAmerica’s 250th anniversary highlights AI, journalism, democracy, and innovation, emphasizing trustworthy public media amid rising misinformation challenges.\\n\\nBy[John Werner](https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnwerner/),\\nContributor\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"aa21fa6fb29b6f48\\\">>>\",\n  \"warning\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8979663fbab70c3b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Fetch\\n---\\nResponse body truncated after 750000 bytes.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8979663fbab70c3b\\\">>>\"\n}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["url","finalUrl","status","contentType","title","extractMode","extractor","externalContent","truncated","length","rawLength","wrappedLength","fetchedAt","tookMs","text","warning"],"status":200,"truncated":false},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783145682347}}
